+ ./cli -h
cli - Sample application to demonstrate the use of needy flags

Usage:
  cli [OPTIONS]
  cli --help | -h
  cli --version | -v

Options:
  --add, -a ALIAS
    Alias to add
    Needs: --command, --target

  --command, -c COMMAND
    Command for the alias
    Needs: --add

  --target, -t TARGET
    Where to add the alias
    Allowed: global, local
    Needs: --add

  --help, -h
    Show this help

  --version, -v
    Show version number

